data.name: infostuff.Text
data.value: This is where you make a PS3 Conf File. in Simple Mode, All you have to do it put in the Content ID. it is 9 letters/numbers. They can be the same but the letters have to be in all caps. The Content ID has to match these things: anything.conf + eboot.bin + param.sfo And it will put that content ID on your PKG. If you dont have all of them match EXACTLY then it will fail. Only use Advanced Mode if you ACTUALLY know what your doing. Have Fun. Donate.
